text.tspan: Various Aspects of the Inner Life — The Proper Heart
Grant me, O Lord, a heart that’s pure,
Your presence seeking with the saints,
Grant me, O Lord, a loving heart,
Draw me each day to turn;
That I for You would yearn,
That I for You would yearn.
Grant me, O Lord, a heart at peace
Our fellowship, in which I walk,
The living of Your kingdom, Lord,
Bring to the earth at last,
Bring to the earth at last!
2018 Melody of Lilies. Used by Permission.
